{"tid":2454841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死左個5歲女既老豆老母算唔算係垃圾MK仔女既天作之合","createTime":"2021-03-20T14:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T12:22:48.000Z","uid":188176,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f71801f2e67947527c4fe78f68d799ba08e4c0bd","tid":2454841,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"MK仔26歲有個8歲仔,5歲女,已離婚,做跟車仔<br />\n應該係中三讀唔成書,做跟車仔搵萬零蚊個月<br />\n但為屌西要威,月月清仙都唔仙下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n17歲就屌到有涵搞到要結婚,18歲生仔,過多兩年仲整多件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌厭之後搵第件要離婚<br />\n搵過件過氣MK妹,萬零蚊5個人唔夠洗仲要投靠人地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMK女27歲有個7歲女,已離婚,無業<br />\n又係中三無讀書,做份幾千蚊垃圾工,諗住食條仔過世<br />\n岩岩出黎做野自己搵幾千,見條MK仔搵一萬多D兩個人岩岩夠洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人屌到有涵搞到要結婚唔辭工,20歲生仔,兩公婆錢唔夠洗唯有離婚<br />\n個MK前夫唔要個女,再搵個跟車仔諗住食佢住佢<br />\n點知廢柴跟車仔一D都無諗過點解決<br />\n仲要搵自己老母幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一樣咁垃圾,有無異議?"},{"pid":"94a642ae1ee7dd2f9a8ba4b6462912454e76d757","tid":2454841,"uid":242537,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"你竟然可以總結到出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係<br />\n呢個畜生既人生真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"5628c3f1df6002e3c90c50fa8eec8e9abd978fb3","tid":2454841,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"問題啦<br />\n條弱智跟車仔點解咁撚鐘意中出 唔戴套？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eee3b41f41c2796d7a679d0e9933232687ac61b","tid":2454841,"uid":3063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"呢啲入到去有人識招呼"},{"pid"